t = int(input())
runner = 1
while runner <= t and t > 0 and (t <= 100):
    inp = input().split()
    L = int(inp[0])
    R = int(inp[1])
    if L < 1 or L > R or R > 10 ** 5:
        break
    count = 0
    for i in range(L, R + 1):
        if i % 10 == 2 or i % 10 == 3 or i % 10 == 9:
            count += 1
    print(count)
    runner += 1
